My dotFiles.

These include configurations for:
        emacs
        git (see ./Makefile)
        xmonad

./Emacs.gitignore is retrieved from https://github.com/github/gitignore

My Emacs config includes (beside .emacs):
    these el files:
        bar-cursor-mode ( http://www.northbound-train.com/emacs.html#MyPackages )
        etags-select & etags-table ( http://emacswiki.org/emacs/EtagsTable )
        less-css-mode ( http://www.emacswiki.org/emacs/LessCssMode )
    these packages:
        auto-complete ( http://cx4a.org/software/auto-complete/ )
        drupal-ide ( http://drupal.org/project/emacs )
        yasnippet ( http://emacswiki.org/emacs/Yasnippet )
    and these elpas:
        coffee-mode
        minimap <3
        nlinum
        windresize

To install:
        make install (that's broken actually... TODO)
To uninstall:
        make uninstall

Dependencies:
        git (make install needs it to download packages)
        xmodmap (to map the Control key to Caps Lock)
